 * NEEDED FOR AUDIO:
 *   - ADSP/CDSP nodes (IORT: \_SB.ADSP.SLM1.ADCM → SMMU0)
 *   - QCOM APR + audio graph bindings
 *
 * PIN VERIFICATION NEEDED:
 *   - I2C1 SCL/SDA (currently gpio55/gpio56 — confirm from schematic)
 *   - I2C2 SCL/SDA (currently gpio15/gpio16 — confirm from schematic)
 *   - I2C9 SCL/SDA (currently gpio47/gpio48 — confirm from schematic)
 *   - UART13 TX/RX  (currently gpio46/gpio47 — confirm from schematic)
 *   - I2C5 SCL/SDA (currently gpio85/gpio86 — confirm from schematic)
 *   - I2C6 SCL/SDA (currently gpio95/gpio96 — confirm from schematic)
 * ==================================================================== */
